g-auto-workers-picket-line-rcna117348">meeting striking UAW workers</a> near Detroit. Biden&#39;s rival, Donald Trump, attempted to match Biden&#39;s move by visiting <a href="https://www.cnbc.com/2023/09/27/uaw-leader-condemns-trump-ahead-of-michigan-visit-during-union-strike.html">a non-union auto parts plant</a> , but was largely ignored and mocked by the union leadership. This probably solidifies Biden&#39;s image as a champion of the Rust Belt and the forgotten working class.</p><p> The UAW strike — which includes demands for 40% higher wages and a shift to a 32-hour workweek — is part of a more general labor revival in the US A wave of major strikes is <a href="https://www.wsj.com/economy/jobs/labor-strikes-multiply-as-workers-score-wins-9c08060e">spreading across the country</a> , including Hollywood writers and actors, airline pilots at American and Delta, UPS delivery workers, Las Vegas service workers, and possibly healthcare workers at Kaiser Permanente. So far, the strike activity in 2023 has already reached levels that haven&#39;t prevailed since the 1980s: </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9099c225-326f-40d7-8b5b-fa6e437759d3_1184x637.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9099c225-326f-40d7-8b5b-fa6e437759d3_1184x637.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F9099c225-326f-40d7-8b5b-fa6e437759d3_1184x637.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp